libuv is a C library used by Node.js to handle:

Event Loop
Thread Pool
Asynchronous I/O operations
Networking
File System operations
Simple Definition

libuv is the engine behind Node.js that provides the Event Loop and Thread Pool, making asynchronous and non-blocking operations possible.


